data.name: CompositionType
desc: specifies which composition should be used when composing a table name.

items.name: ForTableDefinitions
lines: specifies composition of a name to be used in table definitions

items.name: ForIndexDefinitions
lines: specifies composition of a name to be used in index definitions

items.name: ForDataManipulation
lines: specifies composition of a name to be used in data manipulation

items.name: ForProcedureCalls
lines: specifies composition of a name to be used in procedure calls

items.name: ForPrivilegeDefinitions
lines: specifies composition of a name to be used in privilege definitions

items.name: Complete
lines: specifies complete composition of a table name, including catalog and schema (if present), disregarding any database support for catalog and schema in any particular statements
